title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H2 - Apr 9 2022

description:
Romney, Collins, Murkowski are down with KBJ, will vote for Biden SCOTUS nominee. Clay and Buck both said Romney currently "disgusts" them. They refer to him as a coward and a chump, who would do almost anything to get praiseworthy liberal press. The Little Fauch teases return to masks. Utah voters light up the phone lines to rip Mitt Romney. Old Joe, woke warrior for trans child movement. Clay said he thinks there's no way sports fan Joe Biden believes in private that biologically male athletes should be competing in women's sports.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
